data.description: Come see what 924 Middlesex Rd has to offer.  This very well maintained 2 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath townhome is perfect for a starter home or for someone who is looking to  downsize. Enjoy the main floor family room, eat in dinning room and updated kitchen with new cabinets and  Plank flooring throughout. Upstairs has 2 spacious bedrooms and a beautiful fully remodeled bath. In the basement you will find a family/rec room with new flooring , a built in bar, half bathroom, and utility area with washer and dryer. Have fun entertaining on the covered rear deck just off the kitchen. In the back you have the convenience of 2 private parking spaces. The seller with be leaving the main floor family room ,the rear deck and the smaller bedroom tv's for the buyer. The stair lift will be going with the seller .  Don't miss out. Schedule your showing today.
